column8: P0p9wX-ate0PAS ready to defend Kelantan from turning 'blue' or 'orange'Published on Apr 26, 2017PAS deputy president Tuan Ibrahim Tuan Man said two groups were working together to capture Kelantan from PAS.He said recently in Kelantan, the deputy prime minister had announced intentions to turn the state blue and now there have emerged a new group, whose shirts are orange that have also declared that they want the state.
